This place reopened after the owner (Jin) finally got her liquor license back ! Now that they can sell alcohol, they added more k-bar style menu to their old menu. Server told me that jin makes all kimchi so everything with kimchi is good! Everything was DELICIOUS and plates were fun especially cup noodle fried rice. If you are looking for fun k-bar vibe that serves great food, you should definitely try this place!
